### Test 1: Post Mobile App Event (Screen View)
POST https://mobile-metrics-webhook.susui888.workers.dev/api/mobile-telemetry/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "Android",
  "eventType": "SCREEN_VIEW",
  "eventName": "BookDetailScreen",
  "appVersion": "0.1.0",
  "attributes": {
    "book_id": "978-3-16-148410-0",
    "source": "Search_Result_List"
  }
}

### Test 2: Post Mobile App Event (Custom Action)
POST https://mobile-metrics-webhook.susui888.workers.dev/api/mobile-telemetry/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "iOS",
  "eventType": "CUSTOM_EVENT",
  "eventName": "Click_Borrow_Button",
