}

### Test 3: Post Mobile App Event (Error Event)
POST https://mobile-metrics-webhook.susui888.workers.dev/api/mobile-telemetry/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "Android",
  "eventType": "ERROR",
  "eventName": "NetworkTimeoutException",
  "errorMessage": "java.net.SocketTimeoutException: timeout after 10000ms",
  "appVersion": "1.0.0"
}

### Test 4: Post API Performance Metrics
POST https://mobile-metrics-webhook.susui888.workers.dev/api/mobile-telemetry/metrics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "iOS",
  "endpoint": "/api/v1/books/search",
  "method": "GET",
  "statusCode": 200,
  "latencyMs": 145
}